---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="The Quorum | Agora" description="The strategic and theoretical core of the Agora movement.">
  
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 bg-olive-50 text-olive-900 antialiased">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-16">
      
      <header class="space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 border border-amber-200 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-700 font-bold">
          Internal Governance
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-olive-950">
          Quorum
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-olive-800 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">
          “A movement without a theory is a movement that can be bought.”
        </p>
      </header>

      <hr class="border-olive-200" />

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-olive-950">What is Quorum?</h2>
        <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          If you are a member of Agora who has proven your reliability, responsibility, and dedication to our community, your Sponsor may recommend you for the **Quorum**. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
          This is the core organizing body of the movement. As a member of Quorum, you take on greater responsibilities for the project's health, gaining the right to vote on the leadership and strategic direction of the Agora.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="p-8 bg-white border border-olive-200 rounded-3xl shadow-sm space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-olive-950">The Strategic Compass</h2>
        <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
          While Agora is distributed at the chapter level, the <strong class="text-amber-700">Quorum</strong> serves as the movement’s central nervous system. This inner core ensures that our decentralized nature does not lead to drift, co-option, or fragmentation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
          The Quorum is not a ruling body, but a <strong>theoretical vanguard</strong>. Its authority is derived from its absolute responsibility to the Manifesto.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6">
        <div class="p-8 bg-olive-900 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-mono">01. Political Education</h3>
          <p class="text-olive-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Developing the curriculum for Chapter Leaders and Sponsors. The Quorum distills complex critiques of neoliberalism into actionable knowledge for the community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-olive-900 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-mono">02. Campaign Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-olive-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Identifying systemic targets for offline action. The Quorum coordinates national and global “days of exit” to maximize the movement's visibility and impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-olive-900 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-mono">03. Project Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-olive-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Maintaining the app infrastructure. The Quorum manages the code and data of the Agora platform, ensuring it remains a utility for members rather than a product for markets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12 border-t border-olive-200">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-olive-950">How the Quorum Forms</h2>
        <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
          Entry into the Quorum is not through simple election, but through <strong class="text-amber-700">proven stewardship</strong>. It is composed of the movement's most active organizers who have successfully sustained local chapters for a period of no less than two years.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse"></span>
          <p class="text-olive-500 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">
            Status: Active // Members: Undisclosed for security
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="pt-12">
        <a href="/philosophy" class="text-olive-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-bold transition flex items-center gap-2 group">
          <span class="group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform">←</span> Back to Philosophy
        </a>
      </footer>

    </div>
  </article>

</Layout>